      <title>中国的提高利润可能有助于减轻对股票的关税打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/china-s-improving-profits-may-help-soften-tariff-blow-for-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国公司的前景在一场恢复消费的运动季节后，人们的前景变得更加明亮，该季节可能会为当地股票提供急需的垫子，因为它们为美国的关税做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/china-s-improving-profits-may-help-soften-tariff-blow-for-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
